name: Sun in 8th
description:
This is Sun in 8th, part of the "Self Illustrations" series \\

Like a lump of coal that one day becomes a diamond

Embody truth, and become a living example of the light that can emerge from real strength and insight. The breathing and the expired, the graveyard of ashes and rebirth, obsessed with death and the occult, a psychological totem designed to protect against your own mortality.

Size:2000x2000px (300dpi)
